+--- Usage -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|																											|
|	Speed: The speed of which the element is displayed and hidden (default: 300)							|
|	Top: Amount of pixels from the top of the page which the element will show itself (default: 300)		|
|																											|
|	Example basic:																							|
|	$('#element').slithery();																				|
|																											|
|	Example with settings:																					|
|	$('#element').slithery({																				|
|		speed: 2000,																						|
|		top: 1000																							|
|	});																										|
|																											|
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
